   ============================================================================
                         VOICE INTELLIGENCE LAYER
   ============================================================================

   ### Meta Omnilingual ASR ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê (Apache 2.0)
   https://github.com/facebookresearch/fairseq
   Released: November 2025
   - 1,600+ languages (including 500+ low-resource Indian dialects)
   - Zero-shot learning: Extend to 5,400+ languages
   - Model sizes: 300M (2GB), 1B (4GB), 3B (8GB), 7B (14GB)
   - VA21 Default: 1B model for 7GB RAM systems
   Thank you, Meta FAIR team! üôè

   ### OpenAI Whisper / Solus AI (MIT License)
   https://github.com/openai/whisper
   - Offline backup ASR
   - Excellent accuracy for common languages
   Thank you, OpenAI! üôè

   ### Rhasspy Wake Word (MIT License)
   https://github.com/rhasspy/rhasspy
   - Custom wake word detection: "Hey VA21", "Om Vinayaka"
   - Privacy-focused, fully offline
   Thank you, Rhasspy team! üôè

   ### Piper TTS (MIT License)
   https://github.com/rhasspy/piper
   - Fast neural text-to-speech synthesis
   - Low latency for real-time response
   Thank you, Rhasspy/Piper team! üôè

   ### Kokoro TTS (Apache 2.0 License)
   https://github.com/remsky/Kokoro-FastAPI
   - Premium quality neural voices
   - 82M parameter model
   Thank you, Kokoro team! üôè

